My name is [[Samuel Rose]].

[http://holocene.cc Holocene Systems,LLC] is the enterprise that I have created to
help people deal with the complexities of knowledge, understanding,
change, human systems, evolution, foresight, cooperation and
collaboration, and technology.

I have always been interested in effective knowledge synthesis, and I am
interested in exploring and developing the concepts of open knowledge,
open design, and open business.

I also love music, and writing, graphic arts, and
inventing/tinkering/personal fabrication.

